Class IncQueryViewerDataModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.incquery.viewers.runtime.model.ViewerDataModel
      • org.eclipse.incquery.viewers.runtime.model.IncQueryViewerDataModel

  • public class IncQueryViewerDataModel
extends ViewerDataModel
    A ViewerDataModel implementation for IncQuery/EVM model sources. If you instantiate this class yourself, then be sure to dispose() of it once it is not needed anymore.
    Author:
    Zoltan Ujhelyi, Istvan Rath, Csaba Debreceni
